\section{The evaluation dataset}
\label{section:dataset}

The evaluation dataset consists of 101 different historical handwritten texts that were written by people of different ages and of various education backgrounds. The handwritten texts are extracted from books and magazines and are of different content. They cover multiple languages (mostly German and French) and have different font sizes and line-spacing. A total of 1572 words are annotated with their spelling mistakes using the word2vec toolkit\footnote{https://github.com/word2vec/word2vec}. Table~\ref{table:corpora_properties} presents the main properties of the dataset.

