\subsection{Correct text for other languages}
\label{sec:correct-text-other-languages}

Apart from Greek, English and Hebrew, the following languages can be identified by their OCR features:
\begin{enumerate}
\item Italian
\item French
\item Spanish
\item German
\item Arabic
\end{enumerate}

These languages have an OCR model in our repository and are available for our participants.

\subsection{Trial Corrections}
\label{sec:trial-corrections}

To make the task more efficient, the participant is allowed to correct one word. The participant must check the OCR result and correct it if it is wrong. Only one word is allowed to be corrected per document.

